          将课表导入日历以后，Siri, Cortana 这些智能助理也能派上用场啦！更多惊喜，待您发现^_^
        </p>
        <div class="container" style="padding: 0 25px; max-width: 600px;">
          <div class="columns" style="margin-top: 10px;">
            <div class="column has-text-centered">
              <img class="screenshot" src="static/images/screenshot-7.jpg" alt="Siri" style="max-height: 350px;">
            </div>
            <div class="column has-text-centered">
              <img class="screenshot" src="static/images/screenshot-6.png" alt="Cortana" style="max-height: 350px;">
            </div>
